    <item>
      <title>Docs: RPI Touch Screen LCD</title>
      <link>/docs/computer_science/iot/rpi-lcd-display/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/docs/computer_science/iot/rpi-lcd-display/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;br&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;how-to-assemble-rpi-touch-screen-lcd&#34;&gt;How to assemble RPI Touch Screen LCD?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E1lua5mgrJs&#34;&gt;Raspberry Pi 7&amp;quot; Touch Screen LCD - Assembly&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;

&lt;div style=&#34;position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;&#34;&gt;
  &lt;iframe src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/E1lua5mgrJs&#34; style=&#34;position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;&#34; allowfullscreen title=&#34;YouTube Video&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;how-to-adjust-the-screen-brightness&#34;&gt;How to adjust the screen brightness?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;# Adjust brightness
sudo sh -c &#39;echo 90 &amp;gt; /sys/class/backlight/rpi_backlight/brightness&#39;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;how-to-disable-the-screen-saver&#34;&gt;How to disable the screen saver?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo apt-get install xscreensaver
Go to GUI Preferences/Screensaver/DisplayMode/Dropdown/DisableScreenSaver
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;how-to-install-virtual-keyboard-on-rpi&#34;&gt;How to install virtual keyboard on RPI?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo apt-get install matchbox-keyboard -y
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
      </description>
